DataList.LocalizeEN: Is it the Public Safety Bureau's turn?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私を騙そうとしても無駄だ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Trying to trick me is pointless!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 狂犬の名は 一度は聞いたことがあるだろう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You've surely heard the name Mad Dog!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ヴァルキューレ 公安局だ止まれ
DataList.LocalizeEN: Valkyrie Public Safety Bureau! Stop right there!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 動くな、動いたら犯人とみなす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Don't move! Move and you'll be a criminal!

DataList.LocalizeJP: なるほど そんな方法がいい勉強になりました
DataList.LocalizeEN: I see, so that method is...This has been educational.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今日の訓練はこれで十分でしょ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: That should be enough for today's training.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 市民のために 日々精進します。
DataList.LocalizeEN: For the citizens' sake, I'll practice diligence daily.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 局長といえど、鍛錬を怠っては部下の模範になれません
DataList.LocalizeEN: Even as the chief, you can't be a role model to your subordinates if you neglect training.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 世の大人が皆 先生のような方であれば、私たちが仕事をすることもないのに独り言です 気にしないでください。
DataList.LocalizeEN: If every adult in the world was like you Sensei, then we wouldn't have to do any work...Just talking to myself, don't mind me.

DataList.LocalizeJP: いくら 私でも先生を尋問して情報を引き出すのは不可能でしょうね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Interrogating and gaining information from Sensei would be impossible, even for me, wouldn't it. Fufu.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生と生徒の恋愛をおっしゃって、
DataList.LocalizeEN: Romance between teacher and student..?W-What are you saying!?

DataList.LocalizeJP: たまには シャーレを頼れたします。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Occasionally, I have relied on Schale.
